---
title: Seared Salmon & Chive-Lemon Sauce with Golden Roasted Veggies
description: Sometimes, great cooking is a flurry of clever techniques and a dizzying array of ingredients. Other times, it’s the
simplicity of just a few things; chives, butter, lemon, potatoes and a beautifully cooked salmon.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dill-lemon-salmon-potatoes-8249e3db.jpg
